          li Fits virtually any bathtub
          li Holds 100 gallons
          li Fresh for up to 12 weeks
          li Faucet attachment, dispense pump
          li BPA-Free

      section(data-bespoke-state='how')
        h2 How do we get the water?
        a(href='http://www.wikihow.com/Get-Emergency-Drinking-Water-from-a-Water-Heater') WikiHow Guide &#10159;
        p or this video:
        div <iframe width="420" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/mQbwTnW1SL0" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>

      section(data-bespoke-state='secureheater')
        h2 Secure Your Water Heater!
        a(href='http://www.seattle.gov/emergency/library/snap/skills/Earthquake%20Safety%20securing%20water%20heater.pdf') Seattle Earthquake Safety Guide &#10159;

      section(data-bespoke-state='end')
        h2 Sample Food/Water
        Unit 12 has a <a href="http://wiki.duwamish.net/index.php?title=Emergency_Stock_Guide_-_Unit_12">Sample Stock Guide</a> on the Wiki

